---
// CTAFinal.astro — CTA final da landing page
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0A0F14] via-[#0D1B26] to-[#0A1F2E] py-28 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Blobs decorativos -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-[#0097D6]/8 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-[#00D6A0]/8 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center fh-reveal">

    <!-- Ícone -->
    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0097D6] to-[#00D6A0] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 shadow-2xl shadow-[#00D6A0]/20">
      <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight">
      Sua cabeça merece<br /> um descanso.
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-5 text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      Comece a capturar hoje — e termine o dia sabendo que fez o que importava.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="#"
        class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#00D6A0] hover:bg-[#00A87E] text-[#0A0F14] font-black px-10 py-5 rounded-xl text-lg shadow-xl shadow-[#00D6A0]/30 transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105"
      >
        Criar minha conta grátis
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#"
        class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border-2 border-white/20 text-white hover:border-[#0097D6] hover:text-[#0097D6] font-semibold px-10 py-5 rounded-xl text-lg transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Capturar minha primeira tarefa
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-gray-500 text-sm">
      Grátis para sempre · Sem cartão · Web + iOS + Android
    </p>

    <!-- Mini-depoimento final -->
    <div class="mt-14 border-t border-white/10 pt-10">
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg italic max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        "Em 3 dias usando o Focus Hub, minha cabeça ficou mais leve do que em anos de tentativas com outros sistemas."
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mt-4">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0097D6] to-[#00D6A0] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">RA</div>
        <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Rodrigo Almeida · Consultor · São Paulo</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
